  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThe goal of this task is exploring the idea of creating a `QObject event emitter` to register specific events in a `model` comming from it's source of truth (service events) via the `controller - module - view` layered architecture. \r\n\r\nNowadays there is the `EventEmitter` global object that can be used for that propose but here the idea is to explore if it's possible to make it more **context oriented** and just use a specific event emiter object to deal with specific context events. ",
